# Biobase — LLM Wiki (Karpathy pattern)

This workspace implements Andrej Karpathy’s **LLM Wiki** idea ([gist](https://gist.github.com/karpathy/442a6bf555914893e9891c11519de94f)): **raw sources → compiled markdown wiki → schema/skills** that tell agents how to maintain it.

## Where things live

| Piece | Path |
|-------|------|
| **Vault** (compiled wiki) | `wiki/` — `index.md`, `log.md`, `hot.md`, `projects/`, etc. |
| **Raw sources** (immutable) | `docs/llm-wiki-raw/` (e.g. Karpathy gist copy), repo `info.md`, READMEs — add more as needed |
| **Agent skills** (schema + operations) | `obsidian-wiki/.skills/` — symlinked from **`.cursor/skills`** at repo root |
| **Skill bootstrap / routing** | `obsidian-wiki/AGENTS.md`, `obsidian-wiki/CLAUDE.md`, `obsidian-wiki/README.md` |
| **Vault + sources env** | `obsidian-wiki/.env` — from `obsidian-wiki/.env.biobase.example` (copy and adjust paths) |

## Conventions (this repo)

1. **Read vault config:** `obsidian-wiki/.env` → `OBSIDIAN_VAULT_PATH` must point at **`wiki/`** here (`<repo-root>/wiki`).
2. **Skills:** Prefer reading **`obsidian-wiki/.skills/<name>/SKILL.md`** (same content as `.cursor/skills/`).
3. **Compile, don’t only append:** Update existing wiki pages when code/docs change; refresh `index.md`, `log.md`, `hot.md`, and `.manifest.json` per the relevant skill.
4. **Attribution:** Wiki **`hot.md`** / **`index.md`** ask for `agent=` on LLM edits — follow that.

## Quick skill routing

| Intent | Skill |
|--------|--------|
| Initialize or fix vault layout | `wiki-setup` |
| Add a document / folder of sources | `wiki-ingest` |
| Sync **this** repo into `wiki/projects/…` | `wiki-update` |
| Question against compiled pages | `wiki-query` |
| Health check, links, drift | `wiki-lint` |
| Pattern / architecture theory | `llm-wiki` |

For the full table, open `obsidian-wiki/AGENTS.md`.
